{"tid":388472,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有冇急屎經驗？","createTime":"2017-09-05T13:09:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-05T13:31:37.000Z","uid":24339,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6cdf9456327fb485deaf64ca35c431667ef2802e","tid":388472,"uid":24339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:09:39.000Z","msg":"我上星期因為食錯野，係飛機上面瀨左屎，起飛到落機都係1個鐘時間，一起飛個陣就知個肚開始有問題，又多人排隊去廁所，心諗忍到落機應該冇問題，咁就忍啦，忍呀忍...點知準備降落個陣有氣流，部飛機勁un 左一下，呢個時候個屎眼受到咁大衝擊就咇左幾舊屎出黎連同屎水出晒黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我同呀媽講，媽我瀨左野呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 之後用件衫cover 個屎忽頂到落機去廁所<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a547cbdef8367202449dfea4149d013be87992c3","tid":388472,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:19:24.000Z","msg":"咁大個人重瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係你連自己嘅肛門都管理唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死咗佢啦"},{"pid":"ad221b82f86535af4cfb4e86b8a10092c0a82ab3","tid":388472,"uid":72608,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:22:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁大個人重瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 即係你連自己嘅肛門都管理唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 死咗佢啦</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有D屎根本就最多忍5~10分鐘<br />\n再強忍佢會沖出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babfb1feb0310131d12d62e51cf4efc2b2e4d90e","tid":388472,"uid":72608,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:23:08.000Z","msg":"不過我自從幻稚園毋睪業就冇再賴過屎"},{"pid":"fbd3855f88e8e78e8c8a90e7c74f71cf4b89193c","tid":388472,"uid":87971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-05T13:28:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁大個人重瀨屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"